Because its PVP system is the best around. [size=12pt]Like the old KubanPkz, This server includes ::Pure.[/size] Features: - Added Black Mask - Added better KBD - Added more realistic DFS Spec. - Added New spot for Mithrill dragons, made better drops. - Fixed rune C'bow a little. Hits higher. - Added GodWars Teleport - Added More Shops - No more ORB TELES. - No more Runner hats or red Balls as fences. [ Lold ] - Fixed Barrows Mini game, Made it a lot more realistic. - Added more items in the Assault Shops - Took Out all Quest and requirements for weapons. [ Pk Server Duh. ] - Fixed the Neitz Helm, Dragon Scimi, DDS, and D Long log out glitch. [ IDK why it was there lol. ] It is a Pking Server so don't tell me how to run it. I used Universal X Delta Base. Well, i made it first of all. But, i have added a lot!
